a_{n,1} & a_{n,2} & a_{n,3} & \tr & a_{n,n}
\end{array}\right|=\\
 & = & X_{A}\left(\lambda\right)=\left|A-\lambda E\right|=\ous{k=0}n\left(-1\right)^{k}d_{k}\lambda^{k}\ \ \left\{ d_{k}\ -\ \text{число}\right\} 
